subject: College Athletics
Basketball
NCAA Basketball Tournament (Women)
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Before the Big East tournament begins, Coach C. Vivian Stringer said she will not take the Rutgers women's basketball team to the W.N.I.T. if it fails to earn an N.C.A.A. berth.
